    "instructions": [
      "1. Go to Steamworks Partner Site",
      "2. Navigate to your App > Stats & Achievements > Leaderboards",
      "3. Click 'Create Leaderboard' for each board listed above",
      "4. Fill in Name, Sort Method, Display Type",
      "5. Community Name can match the name",
      "6. Set 'Writes' to 'Trusted' to prevent cheating",
      "7. Set 'Reads' to 'Public'",
      "8. Save and publish changes"
